{"tid":767800,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"試過唔見左咩野搞到好騰雞？","createTime":"2018-08-04T23:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T16:41:11.000Z","uid":43507,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"261ae2035379d86af52e817e61a68a16beac7ee3","tid":767800,"uid":43507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T23:10:20.000Z","msg":"以前中學去班會旅行唔見左銀包<br />\n身份證 八達通 錢都冇<br />\n得番幾蚊係身，回程離屋企都個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身唔覺唔見左，到要走搭車先發現冇八達通，跟住用幾蚊上左車先發現真係唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一下即刻想落車番去搵，個陣唔見幾百蚊對我黎講已經天文數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿sir 話想陪我去搵，我都say no 廢事麻煩人<br />\n最後阿sir 堅持話要陪，話我冇錢點樣番屋企，同咪唔想dum 低d 學生<br />\n跟住佢陪我番去踩二人車周圍搵(旅行戈到係踩單車既)<br />\n雖然最後都搵唔到，去左警署報案<br />\n不過真係好多謝阿sir 你！！最後仲要借左錢俾我番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8839fee4cdb88690be037d3ce48f546c96dae8","tid":767800,"uid":7390,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"准考證"},{"pid":"9ae1f6e0ec0eb78d7f862747067f816a1a2deed3","tid":767800,"uid":174537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T23:15:06.000Z","msg":"旅行唔見passport <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e6b4ecb342eaac02df0971d5cd1bf08cb52c10","tid":767800,"uid":28170,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T23:16:19.000Z","msg":"上兩個星期去睇子華<br />\n<br />\n上網買兩張飛<br />\n佢連埋收據會出三張野<br />\n<br />\n去到入場先知拎左張收劇當飛<br />\n<br />\n女朋友嬲到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最黎靠信用卡資料入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dac7c0df1f3ef0116b03da90bf66afcf10aebf7","tid":767800,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"中出完唔見咗個dom<br />\n<br />\n利申：9吹"},{"pid":"65c2bc8601aa56f5148322c45